This data source provides a list of EDAS deploy groups in an Alibaba Cloud account according to the specified filters.

> **NOTE:** Available in 1.82.0+

```csharp
class MyStack : Stack

    public MyStack()

        {
            AppId = "xxx",
            Ids = 
            {
                "xxx",
            },
            OutputFile = "groups.txt",
        }));
        this.FirstGroupName = groups.Apply(groups => groups.Groups[0].GroupName);
    }

    [Output("firstGroupName")]
    public Output<string> FirstGroupName { get; set; }
}
```

```go
package main

	"github.com/pulumi/pulumi-alicloud/sdk/v2/go/alicloud/edas"

func main() {

			AppId: "xxx",
			Ids: []string{
				"xxx",
			},
			OutputFile: &opt0,
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		ctx.Export("firstGroupName", groups.Groups[0].GroupName)
		return nil
	})
}
```
